Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.86,0:00:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.81,0:00:19.64,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.71,0:00:23.98,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.75,0:00:32.39,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.50,0:00:41.10,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.74,0:00:50.30,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.38,0:00:51.87,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.95,0:00:56.88,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.85,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.92,0:01:03.65,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.73,0:01:07.39,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.06,0:01:16.37,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.74,0:01:19.90,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.21,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定 一定 一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.44,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.51,0:01:28.51,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我下車！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.56,0:01:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙真是吵死人了\N給我安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.69,0:01:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼樣都沒關係\N只要放了帕希菲卡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.46,0:01:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是吵得太過份\N我就殺了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...會怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.62,0:02:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那個廢棄公主\N做過那麼壞的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.70,0:02:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#19 母親嘆息的無言歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.84,0:02:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？等一下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.58,0:02:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.02,0:02:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道要我用這個方便嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是監獄嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，本來就是監獄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就連澡都沒得洗了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.93,0:02:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐...薇妮雅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.60,0:02:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...請問一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.91,0:03:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.25,0:03:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到廢棄公主了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.92,0:03:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.92,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.36,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是她並不承認自己是廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是假的也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.03,0:04:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是"我們"抓到了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.80,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主都已經抓到手了\N我們還要袖手旁觀嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.21,0:04:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離公主滿16歲還有200小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多觀察一下狀況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.21,0:04:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像可以看到愚蠢生物\N做出有趣的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄人類只是浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說是毫無意義的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我們的人格模型\N就是那些殘酷又壞心腸的人類喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你別忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒你們的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡小姐怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麼多，快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，喂，等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開門！給我開門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.89,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開門！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們開門...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們開門...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約好的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對會保護...帕希菲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他...約好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.12,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做真的好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就不會被迫解散了\N應該是好的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小克里，吉兒姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說佛爾西斯王子\N要被趕到聖都去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.06,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子好像多次向國王請求\N要更謹慎處理廢棄公主的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且王子一直進言希望不要戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王大概想把礙手礙腳的王子\N扔得遠遠的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...克里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算部隊沒了\N我們還是會跟你走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.09,0:05:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟希望怎麼做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你那邊也接到通知了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到了，收到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.96,0:06:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這表示已經抓到\N那個什麼廢棄公主了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以悠閒一段時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為上面已經取消搜索命令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主人在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在大概已經被處決了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.95,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她可是毀滅世界的劇毒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說長得很醜又很凶惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.69,0:06:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子，你的右手在幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.87,0:06:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必你應該有所覺悟了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險的徵兆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過度焦躁使得行動毫無計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是讓我焦躁的理由之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是夏儂．卡蘇魯，對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.76,0:07:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是王國軍諜報部\N特別任務處理班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑之鷹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是班長路克‧史達姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.53,0:07:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你跟我們走一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在那邊的女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.47,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秩序守護者閣下也請一起同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我想先說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前我們對你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是對秩序守護者這邊的勢力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有敵對的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把這次的事當成對你們的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個麻煩的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過無所謂，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.21,0:08:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我知道很難逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是沒想到會那麼快...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況連夏儂人在哪裡\N都還不知道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會想辦法救她出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.95,0:08:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼救呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劫獄或是大逃亡之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦法很多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得聽不太懂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就用拉蔻兒小姐的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.29,0:08:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在還不清楚帕希菲卡的狀況下\N不能隨便採取行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認識的那個異教檢察官呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被叫到王城裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能見到貝爾肯斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.34,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許能知道一些帕希菲卡的狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.14,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，奉國王之命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.11,0:08:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請殿下立刻遷居到聖都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王都的情勢越來越嚴峻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.46,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了殿下的安危著想\N陛下認為這樣做會比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說抓到廢棄公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.56,0:08:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在離開之前\N能不能讓我看妹妹一眼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.25,0:09:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看妳好像很痛苦的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.88,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事，倒是妳自己沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.18,0:09:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，謝謝姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.62,0:09:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣\N我已經有一對兒女了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳幾歲了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾歲了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.76,0:09:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喪失記憶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.97,0:09:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我實在弄不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.10,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會被抓來這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.64,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然說我是廢棄公主\N真是讓我傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.78,0:09:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨，妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨妳為什麼會在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.72,0:10:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷把大家要殺的人放走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們逼我說出那個人在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人既然已經被抓到了\N那我對他們就沒有用處了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是妳很重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被抓到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.93,0:10:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的手...好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的手好溫暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貝達修達爾將軍要我傳話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.77,0:10:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠邀請到你們\N讓他感到非常光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒空聽這些沒用的社交辭令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事快說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:10:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是秩序守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使借用了人類的外型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.09,0:11:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是不懂人類的常識和禮節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.62,0:11:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們才無禮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特地找我們過來\N只是想說風涼話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點，夏儂．卡蘇魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你到這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將軍，我把人帶到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就直說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.55,0:11:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想跟你聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.33,0:11:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為秩序守護者的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗中介入我們的世界\N操縱歷史至今
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我們已經調查清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管我們\N要不要原諒秩序守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都要向基亞特進軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.78,0:12:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後成為這個世界的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是什麼原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.62,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，廢棄公主似乎是\N秩序守護者唯一的威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們現在手上\N正掌握著廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿我妹妹當談判籌碼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把妹妹還給我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主平安無事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.24,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像擁有足以跟\N秩序守護者匹敵的戰鬥能力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.52,0:12:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是肯幫忙\N我們很輕易就能稱霸世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.72,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.89,0:12:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想跟秩序守護者談判？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.46,0:12:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他們讓你們支配世界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我認為這樣做很正確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對誰來說很正確？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不打算幫助我們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫助？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.71,0:13:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最重視的妹妹\N現在還在我們手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我會再找你談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前請你好好考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.09,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秩序守護者？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.36,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是叫作龍機神的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.30,0:13:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒笨到會從這裡逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.44,0:13:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在剛剛那間休息室等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.94,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.98,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡似乎在\N這座王城的監牢當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不能做應該很痛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.22,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到妳會考慮到我的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想助你一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.03,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我好像是妳的主人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.76,0:13:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.97,0:14:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是憑自己的自由意志\N想要幫助你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要的時候就呼喚我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在你身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.86,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛羅蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.36,0:14:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要多久才能啟動？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還剩三十小時左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.50,0:14:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能在那麼短的時間內\N就做到將近完工的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說都是跟我們相同的人類\N所製造過的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.08,0:14:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛收到賽菲莉絲的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.61,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡．卡蘇魯被王國抓到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛羅蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.49,0:14:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三小時後啟動龍巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.04,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管試多少次都找不到夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.91,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有某種東西在干擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.18,0:15:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說秩序守護者在他旁邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.25,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能默默祈禱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求神只是浪費時間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡無濟於事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有我一個人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡...\N要是平安無事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會有事的對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.48,0:15:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在這種地方做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道都是這種痛苦的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不應該到王都來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.65,0:16:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下定決心離開塔爾斯鎮\N結果卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們說了些什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許正如妳說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.18,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類既愚蠢又膚淺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.01,0:16:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上貪得無饜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜說這種話的我也是人類啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.05,0:16:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果放著不管\N人類這個種族總有一天會滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.16,0:16:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們就是為了\N讓人類延續下去而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡滿16歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候會變成什麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界會消失嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是只有人類會毀滅呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也掌握不到那個系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.71,0:17:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是完成交付給我們的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.85,0:17:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊\N我就在那邊的小劇場打工了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我演什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然是馬腳，馬腳喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.99,0:17:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我演公主也就算了\N演馬腳實在太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，我真想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我演馬腳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.13,0:17:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我想看妳那樣跟許多人\N快快樂樂生活的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得阿姨說過妳有個女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直沒有見過面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.38,0:17:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女兒還在襁褓之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.12,0:17:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拋棄她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連名字都還沒幫她取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.52,0:17:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一旦取了名字\N我就會不忍心拋棄她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.63,0:17:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我無論如何\N都沒辦法把她留在身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳女兒現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輾轉得知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.77,0:18:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她長大成為一個\N無憂無慮又活潑開朗的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.65,0:18:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直祈禱有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.71,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能再見到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.18,0:18:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以見到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.96,0:18:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有個想見的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.09,0:18:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個不討人喜歡的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去澡堂老是讓我等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肖像畫也畫得不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.60,0:18:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有一點點溫柔的地方啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.87,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經到了會喜歡上\N某個人的年紀了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上是喜歡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.44,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊，吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的阿姨好像很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去叫醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.43,0:19:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼...名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.64,0:19:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫帕美拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以離開這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放棄就等於輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨也一起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.35,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事...想拜託妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.67,0:20:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望最後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以聽妳叫我一聲媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.01,0:20:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代替我的女兒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，我叫不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要是叫了\N阿姨，妳就會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.86,0:20:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，我現在就想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，喂，不可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕美拉，對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不可以，回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.11,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳，振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:17.93,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.01,0:21:23.31,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.58,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.65,0:21:36.35,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.42,0:21:41.19,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.26,0:21:44.63,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.70,0:21:49.66,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.74,0:21:56.27,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.34,0:21:59.57,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.65,0:22:02.95,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.02,0:22:09.51,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.59,0:22:16.26,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.33,0:22:21.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.60,0:22:28.73,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.61,0:22:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡被帶出牢房\N來到國王面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.11,0:22:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，國王好像非常害怕帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.35,0:22:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是什麼都不怕的\N貝達修達爾將軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.38,0:22:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎想利用帕希菲卡\N跟秩序守護者夕紫做交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.95,0:22:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要跟神一樣的人談判\N真是太大膽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.62,0:22:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主 下一回\N「神聖崩壞的序曲」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.13,0:22:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待